| Stop condition | `<when-to-stop-waiting-or-roll-back>` |
| Validation owner | `<validation-owner>` |
| Timestamp | `<timestamp-and-timezone>` |

Avoid these actions unless the incident process explicitly approves them:

- `FLUSHDB`
- `FLUSHALL`
- Broad wildcard deletion
- Repeated Redis scaling attempts while the cluster is already stuck in `modifying`
- Large-scale `CLIENT KILL` without reconnect controls
- Increasing worker or pod replicas while Redis is already under pressure

